its a No Framework PHP MVC.
Loaded by loader,router,apc,pdo,input sanitizer, and
can be use for mockup or simple web apps

//Rules
Load your model on your controller file or maybe view file, 
and load a controller on your view file.

// Load module
load::c('[controller name]');
load::m('[model name]');
load::v('[view name]');
load::l('[library name]');

// Define your route on index.php file
// no htaccess: http://localhost.com/index.php/home
// with htaccess: http://localhost.com/home
// Adding route
// load::l('router')->add('/[uri path]','[view name]');

load::l('router')->add('/','home');
//regex route
load::l('router')->add('/home/(.+)/([0-9]+)','home');
//run
load::l('router')->run();